STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Joseph WATSON, Defendant-Petitioner. C-438 September Term 2017
080215 Supreme Court of New Jersey. December 13, 2017

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-005066-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
